# problem-specific runtime parameters
PWave_Lambda     0.5           # plane wave wavelength
PWave_Amp        1.0           # plane wave amplitude 
PWave_Phase0     0.0           # plane wave phase constant
PWave_XYZ          0           # plane wave direction (0/1/2/3 --> x/y/z/diagonal)
PWave_LSR          1           # plane wave direction (<0/0/>0 --> negative direction/standing wave/positive direction)  
